{"id": "anc_fab_menu", "modality": "animations", "name": "Fab Menu", "task": {"description": "Create a self-contained 1920x1080 HTML animation (inline CSS, NO <canvas>) of a floating action button (FAB) in the BOTTOM-RIGHT corner. Over ~2s it expands into a speed-dial of FOUR equal-size sub-action buttons that fan upward in a vertical column above the FAB (each with a small label to its left), then the FAB icon rotates 45deg. All buttons must remain fully on screen near the corner.", "requirements": ["The FAB stays anchored in the bottom-right corner, fully within the viewport, at every frame", "Four equal-size sub-action buttons appear over time, fanning upward above the FAB", "All four sub-buttons stay fully within the viewport (none clipped at the top or right edge)", "The sub-buttons are vertically aligned in a column with uniform gaps", "Sub-buttons do not overlap each other or the FAB", "Each sub-button's label sits beside it without overlapping another button"], "difficulty": "hard"}, "runs": [{"run": 1, "ss_n_defects": 0, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 4215, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 1, "rv_total_tokens": 4215}, {"run": 2, "ss_n_defects": 0, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 4215, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 1, "rv_total_tokens": 4215}, {"run": 3, "ss_n_defects": 0, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 4215, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 1, "rv_total_tokens": 3625}], "ss_img": "images/animations/anc_fab_menu_ss.jpg", "rv_img": "images/animations/anc_fab_menu_rv.jpg", "ss_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>FAB Speed Dial Animation</title>\n    <style>\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            width: 1920px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        .fab-container {\n            position: fixed;\n            bottom: 32px;\n            right: 32px;\n            z-index: 1000;\n        }\n\n        .fab {\n            width: 64px;\n            height: 64px;\n            background: #ff4757;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(255, 71, 87, 0.4);\n            transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 10;\n        }\n\n        .fab:hover {\n            transform: scale(1.1);\n            box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(255, 71, 87, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        .fab-icon {\n            width: 24px;\n            height: 24px;\n            fill: white;\n            transition: transform 2s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);\n        }\n\n        .fab.expanded .fab-icon {\n            transform: rotate(45deg);\n        }\n\n        .speed-dial {\n            position: absolute;\n            bottom: 80px;\n            right: 0;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            gap: 16px;\n            align-items: flex-end;\n        }\n\n        .speed-dial-item {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            gap: 16px;\n            opacity: 0;\n            transform: translateY(20px) scale(0.8);\n            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);\n        }\n\n        .speed-dial-item.show {\n            opacity: 1;\n            transform: translateY(0) scale(1);\n        }\n\n        .speed-dial-item:nth-child(1) { transition-delay: 0.1s; }\n        .speed-dial-item:nth-child(2) { transition-delay: 0.2s; }\n        .speed-dial-item:nth-child(3) { transition-delay: 0.3s; }\n        .speed-dial-item:nth-child(4) { transition-delay: 0.4s; }\n\n        .speed-dial-label {\n            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);\n            color: #2c3e50;\n            padding: 8px 16px;\n            border-radius: 24px;\n            font-size: 14px;\n            font-weight: 500;\n            white-space: nowrap;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);\n        }\n\n        .speed-dial-button {\n            width: 48px;\n            height: 48px;\n            background: white;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\n            transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);\n        }\n\n        .speed-dial-button:hover {\n            transform: scale(1.1);\n            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        .speed-dial-button svg {\n            width: 20px;\n            height: 20px;\n            fill: #2c3e50;\n        }\n\n        .speed-dial-button.edit { background: #3742fa; }\n        .speed-dial-button.edit svg { fill: white; }\n\n        .speed-dial-button.share { background: #2ed573; }\n        .speed-dial-button.share svg { fill: white; }\n\n        .speed-dial-button.delete { background: #ff4757; }\n        .speed-dial-button.delete svg { fill: white; }\n\n        .speed-dial-button.settings { background: #ffa502; }\n        .speed-dial-button.settings svg { fill: white; }\n\n        .backdrop {\n            position: fixed;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\n            pointer-events: none;\n            transition: background 0.3s ease;\n            z-index: 5;\n        }\n\n        .backdrop.show {\n            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            pointer-events: auto;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"backdrop\" id=\"backdrop\"></div>\n    \n    <div class=\"fab-container\">\n        <div class=\"speed-dial\" id=\"speedDial\">\n            <div class=\"speed-dial-item\">\n                <div class=\"speed-dial-label\">Settings</div>\n                <div class=\"speed-dial-button settings\">\n                    <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n                        <path d=\"M12,15.5A3.5,3.5 0 0,1 8.5,12A3.5,3.5 0 0,1 12,8.5A3.5,3.5 0 0,1 15.5,12A3.5,3.5 0 0,1 12,15.5M19.43,12.97C19.47,12.65 19.5,12.33 19.5,12C19.5,11.67 19.47,11.34 19.43,11L21.54,9.37C21.73,9.22 21.78,8.95 21.66,8.73L19.66,5.27C19.54,5.05 19.27,4.96 19.05,5.05L16.56,6.05C16.04,5.66 15.5,5.32 14.87,5.07L14.5,2.42C14.46,2.18 14.25,2 14,2H10C9.75,2 9.54,2.18 9.5,2.42L9.13,5.07C8.5,5.32 7.96,5.66 7.44,6.05L4.95,5.05C4.73,4.96 4.46,5.05 4.34,5.27L2.34,8.73C2.22,8.95 2.27,9.22 2.46,9.37L4.57,11C4.53,11.34 4.5,11.67 4.5,12C4.5,12.33 4.53,12.65 4.57,12.97L2.46,14.63C2.27,14.78 2.22,15.05 2.34,15.27L4.34,18.73C4.46,18.95 4.73,19.03 4.95,18.95L7.44,17.94C7.96,18.34 8.5,18.68 9.13,18.93L9.5,21.58C9.54,21.82 9.75,22 10,22H14C14.25,22 14.46,21.82 14.5,21.58L14.87,18.93C15.5,18.68 16.04,18.34 16.56,17.94L19.05,18.95C19.27,19.03 19.54,18.95 19.66,18.73L21.66,15.27C21.78,15.05 21.73,14.78 21.54,14.63L19.43,12.97Z\"/>\n                    </svg>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"speed-dial-item\">\n                <div class=\"speed-dial-label\">Delete</div>\n                <div class=\"speed-dial-button delete\">\n                    <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n                        <path d=\"M19,4H15.5L14.5,3H9.5L8.5,4H5V6H19M6,19A2,2 0 0,0 8,21H16A2,2 0 0,0 18,19V7H6V19Z\"/>\n                    </svg>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"speed-dial-item\">\n                <div class=\"speed-dial-label\">Share</div>\n                <div class=\"speed-dial-button share\">\n                    <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n                        <path d=\"M18,16.08C17.24,16.08 16.56,16.38 16.04,16.85L8.91,12.7C8.96,12.47 9,12.24 9,12C9,11.76 8.96,11.53 8.91,11.3L15.96,7.19C16.5,7.69 17.21,8 18,8A3,3 0 0,0 21,5A3,3 0 0,0 18,2A3,3 0 0,0 15,5C15,5.24 15.04,5.47 15.09,5.7L8.04,9.81C7.5,9.31 6.79,9 6,9A3,3 0 0,0 3,12A3,3 0 0,0 6,15C6.79,15 7.5,14.69 8.04,14.19L15.16,18.34C15.11,18.55 15.08,18.77 15.08,19C15.08,20.61 16.39,21.91 18,21.91C19.61,21.91 20.92,20.61 20.92,19A2.92,2.92 0 0,0 18,16.08Z\"/>\n                    </svg>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"speed-dial-item\">\n                <div class=\"speed-dial-label\">Edit</div>\n                <div class=\"speed-dial-button edit\">\n                    <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n                        <path d=\"M20.71,7.04C21.1,6.65 21.1,6 20.71,5.63L18.37,3.29C18,2.9 17.35,2.9 16.96,3.29L15.12,5.12L18.87,8.87M3,17.25V21H6.75L17.81,9.93L14.06,6.18L3,17.25Z\"/>\n                    </svg>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"fab\" id=\"fab\">\n            <svg class=\"fab-icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n                <path d=\"M19,13H13V19H11V13H5V11H11V5H13V11H19V13Z\"/>\n            </svg>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <script>\n        const fab = document.getElementById('fab');\n        const speedDial = document.getElementById('speedDial');\n        const backdrop = document.getElementById('backdrop');\n        const speedDialItems = document.querySelectorAll('.speed-dial-item');\n        \n        let isExpanded = false;\n        \n        // Auto-expand after 1 second\n        setTimeout(() => {\n            expandSpeedDial();\n        }, 1000);\n        \n        function expandSpeedDial() {\n            if (isExpanded) return;\n            \n            isExpanded = true;\n            fab.classList.add('expanded');\n            backdrop.classList.add('show');\n            \n            // Show speed dial items with staggered animation\n            speedDialItems.forEach((item, index) => {\n                setTimeout(() => {\n                    item.classList.add('show');\n                }, index * 100);\n            });\n        }\n        \n        function collapseSpeedDial() {\n            if (!isExpanded) return;\n            \n            isExpanded = false;\n            fab.classList.remove('expanded');\n            backdrop.classList.remove('show');\n            \n            // Hide speed dial items\n            speedDialItems.forEach(item => {\n                item.classList.remove('show');\n            });\n        }\n        \n        // Click handlers\n        fab.addEventListener('click', (e) => {\n            e.stopPropagation();\n            if (isExpanded) {\n                collapseSpeedDial();\n            } else {\n                expandSpeedDial();\n            }\n        });\n        \n        backdrop.addEventListener('click', () => {\n            collapseSpeedDial();\n        });\n        \n        // Prevent speed dial clicks from closing\n        speedDial.addEventListener('click', (e) => {\n            e.stopPropagation();\n        });\n        \n        // Add click handlers for speed dial buttons\n        document.querySelectorAll('.speed-dial-button').forEach(button => {\n            button.addEventListener('click', (e) => {\n                e.stopPropagation();\n                // Add your action logic here\n                console.log('Speed dial action clicked');\n                collapseSpeedDial();\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>", "rv_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>FAB Speed Dial Animation</title>\n    <style>\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            width: 1920px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        .fab-container {\n            position: fixed;\n            bottom: 32px;\n            right: 32px;\n            z-index: 1000;\n        }\n\n        .fab {\n            width: 64px;\n            height: 64px;\n            background: #ff4757;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(255, 71, 87, 0.4);\n            transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 10;\n        }\n\n        .fab:hover {\n            transform: scale(1.1);\n            box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(255, 71, 87, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        .fab-icon {\n            width: 24px;\n            height: 24px;\n            fill: white;\n            transition: transform 2s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);\n        }\n\n        .fab.expanded .fab-icon {\n            transform: rotate(45deg);\n        }\n\n        .speed-dial {\n            position: absolute;\n            bottom: 80px;\n            right: 0;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            gap: 16px;\n            align-items: flex-end;\n        }\n\n        .speed-dial-item {\n         